
# Significant earthquakes

The most significant earthquakes from last month.


## Authors

- [@walterqf](https://www.github.com/walterqf)


## Installation

Install my-project with npm

```bash
  Open terminal
  Go to project path
  run npm install
```
    
## API Reference

#### Get all items

```http
  GET http://localhost:3000/api/earthquakes
```

| Parameter | Type     | Description                |
| :-------- | :------- | :------------------------- |
| `id` | `string` | **Required**. |
